Reasoning: The paper deals with a multi-hop relay channel with multiple antenna terminals, which is a topic related to information theory (cs.IT) and networking and internet architecture (cs.NI). The analysis of diversity-multiplexing tradeoff (DMT) is a common theme in communication systems (cs.COMM) and system and control theory (cs.SY). The use of multiple antennas also falls under the category of multimedia (cs.MM).
